    "Automated Prompt Engineer (Zhou et al., 2023) optimizes prompts with the help of an LLM, reducing its susceptibility to adversarial attacks and jailbreaks that overcome the safeguards for ethical use of these systems (Zhou et al., 2024).",
    "At the same time, there is still much work to do: LLM-based automatic prompt optimizers struggle to identify the true causes of errors, and we should rather focus on an automated behavior optimization paradigm (Ma et al., 2024).",
    "Prompt optimization is already a step ahead compared to the quantification of our metrics, and we hope that this work will inspire new prompting strategies that do not focus on the sole evaluation of task accuracy.",
